# Campus Marche — Monorepo Environment Variables
#
# This is a pnpm workspace monorepo. Each app has its own .env file:
#
#   apps/api/.env      → NestJS backend (copy from apps/api/.env.example)
#   apps/web/.env      → Next.js frontend (copy from apps/web/.env.example)
#
# Quick start:
#   cp apps/api/.env.example apps/api/.env
#   cp apps/web/.env.example apps/web/.env
#   # Then fill in DATABASE_URL, JWT_SECRET, and PAYSTACK_SECRET_KEY
